Patch Set 1: Workflow-1

FYI, here's an early stab at this. The property protection stuff confuses me a little, and I'm wondering why some of those tests are looking for CONFLICT instead of FORBIDDEN in some cases.

I re-realized while doing this that all our functional tests run with every policy element disabled (i.e. wide-open). The stack underneath this is largely to allow us to take the default so we can even test the changes we make to update(). I set the test policy to the default here while I was testing things, but this should probably just comment out modify_image to take the default automatically.
